For anyone who doesn't have a scale, I tried the recipe and it's DELICIOUS. here's what I used: 
1.5 medium eggs
4 tbsp sugar
1/3 tsp salt
2.15 tsp honey 
3/4 unsalted butter stick
5 tbsp whole milk
3/4 cake flour
1 tsp baking powder
2 round tbsp cocoa powder
3.5 tbsp almond powder 
Chocolate chips 
*you can make cake flour by filling a a cup of all propose flourthen taking out 2 tbsp of it and replace it with 2 tbsp corn starch then sift twice. After that measure the amount you need and save the rest.
* I didn't have almond powder so I putpeeled almonds in a food processor for a few seconds (too much time will turn it to paste) then sift it.
